    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and factory-tuned variable valve timing (VANOS). Power is sent to the rear wheels through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with an emphasis on structural integrity, including a recent subframe reinforcement and bushing refresh. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the visceral, high-RPM engagement these cars are known for. It sits on staggered alloy wheels with a suspension geometry optimized for communicative feedback and neutral handling characteristics.",
