    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and reliability, maintained with a 'maintenance-first' mindset. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of respectful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is stout. It has a full service history, with a recent oil change and brake pad replacement performed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. It drives straight, handles tight, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a turn-key example for a buyer who values mechanical integrity and a clean, presentable aesthetic without the 'mint' showroom markup.",
